features: High quality movement: The external material of our washing machine is made of high-quality ABS material,which is lightweight and durable. It is equipped with a pure copper motor,which has greater torque and high-speed centrifugal operation,driving the washing rhythm of the wave wheel. The cleaning is more powerful,and there is a suction cup at the bottom,which allows you to install it in buckets,washbasins,sinks,etc. It is easy to install and will not fall off.

Three speed remote control use: Intelligent three speed timing can meet your different needs for laundry. The three speed time adjustment (10 minutes for standard washing,20 minutes for soft washing,and 30 minutes for strong washing) allows you to select the gear according to the degree of dirt on the clothes. After cleaning,the power will automatically cut off,and there are no safety hazards. You can use it with confidence

Intelligent hand washing/effective decontamination: The hand washing spiral wave wheel,combined with precise washing speed,cleans 360 ° without dead corners,making it cleaner and more thorough than hand washing. It can effectively remove stains and liberate your hands. Even delicate clothing such as silk and chiffon can be washed with confidence,and its design noise is very low,so you dont have to worry about disturbing your rest or sleep.

Suitable for cleaning a variety of clothes: Our turbo washing machine is very suitable for cleaning socks,underwear,towels,intimate small clothes,baby clothes,saliva wipes and other light and small items. We provide convenient plugs that you can use anywhere,such as buckets,sinks,washbasins,etc

Business/travel laundry is more convenient: Our turbo washing machine is compact,lightweight,and does not take up a lot of space,making it very easy to carry. When you go on a trip,you can easily wash clothes with it. It is not only a laundry gadget,but also a convenient and durable tool that can be installed and taken with you,free of constraints
